<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>EMA515_05_SU_0004_s</title>

  <!-- 공통 js-->
  <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>

  <!-- 공통 css-->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

  <!-- 개별 -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema515_05.css" />
</head>

<body>
  <div id="app_wrap" class="ema515_05_su_0004">
    <section class="title type2">
      <h2 data-head="2_light_purple" class="fraction_box_title">
        <div class="fraction_txt_wrap">
          <div class="fraction_txt" lang="y">
            <div class="operation_box ml_0">
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span>2</span>
                <span>9</span>
              </div>
              -
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span>1</span>
                <span>6</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            을 어떻게 계산하는지 알아봅시다.
          </div>
        </div>
      </h2>
    </section>

    <section class="contents paging_layout">
      <div class="input_area">
        <article class="page page_1">
          <h3 lang="y">두 분모의 곱을 공통분모로 하여 통분한 후 계산해 보세요.</h3>

          <div class="container">
            <div class="operations">
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span>2</span>
                <span>9</span>
              </div>
              -
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span>1</span>
                <span>6</span>
              </div>
              =
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span>2×6</span>
                <span>9×6</span>
              </div>
              -
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span>
                  1×
                  <div class="input_wrap">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="9"></math-field>
                  </div>
                </span>
                <span>6×9</span>
              </div>
              =
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span>12</span>
                <span>54</span>
              </div>
              -
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span>
                  <div class="input_wrap">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="9"></math-field>
                  </div>
                </span>
                <span>54</span>
              </div>
              =
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span>
                  <div class="input_wrap">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="3"></math-field>
                  </div>
                </span>
                <span>54</span>
              </div>
              =
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span>
                  <div class="input_wrap">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="1"></math-field>
                  </div>
                </span>
                <span>18</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="page page_2">
          <h3 lang="y">두 분모의 최소공배수를 공통분모로 하여 통분한 후 계산해 보세요.</h3>
          <div class="question_box justify_center">
            <div class="container">
              <div class="operations">
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <span>2</span>
                  <span>9</span>
                </div>
                -
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <span>1</span>
                  <span>6</span>
                </div>
                =
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <span>2×2</span>
                  <span>9×2</span>
                </div>
                -
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <span>
                    1×
                    <div class="input_wrap">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="3"></math-field>
                    </div>
                  </span>
                  <span>6×3</span>
                </div>
                =
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <span>4</span>
                  <span>18</span>
                </div>
                -
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <span>
                    <div class="input_wrap">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="3"></math-field>
                    </div>
                  </span>
                  <span>18</span>
                </div>
                =
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <span>
                    <div class="input_wrap">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="1"></math-field>
                    </div>
                  </span>
                  <span>18</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="page page_3">
          <h3 lang="y">앞의 두 방법을 비교하여 이야기해 보세요.</h3>
          <div class="question_box justify_center">
            <div class="input_wrap">
              <math-field class="textarea"></math-field>
              <ol class="example_box">
                <li lang="y">두 분모의 곱을 공통분모로 하여 통분하면 공통분모를 구하기 쉽습니다.</li>
                <li lang="y">두 분모의 최소공배수를 공통분모로 하여 통분하면 계산한 결과를 약분할 필요가 없거나 간단합니다.</li>
            </div>
            </ol>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>

      <div class="btn_area">
        <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
        <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
        <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        <button class="btnSubmit">확인</button>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</body>

</html>